   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;Eutychides to Zenon greeting. Know that [- - -]. Be good enough then [to write to] Antipatros(?) what he must do and also to Epharmostos to stand by [and not be(?)] absent when the case is tried, less they be undone. For the two [have not even got counsellors(?)] to talk to their opponents. Intervene then [- - -] and talk to Tharsylos too, if it [seem - - -]. Farewell. The 4th.;;(Verso);;To Zenon.</ab>
         </div>
